## Remedies for Infringement of Data Subject Rights

Data subjects may seek remedies for personal information infringement through the Personal Information Dispute Mediation Committee, the Personal Information Infringement Report Center of KISA, and other relevant agencies.

- Personal Information Dispute Mediation Committee — 1833-6972 (www.kopico.go.kr)
- Personal Information Infringement Report Center — 118 (privacy.kisa.or.kr)
- Supreme Prosecutors' Office — 1301 (www.spo.go.kr)
- Korean National Police Agency — 182 (ecrm.police.go.kr)

